{"tid":2398912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五年前嘅今日，就係魚蛋革命嘅日子","createTime":"2021-02-07T16:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T16:01:07.000Z","uid":5843,"like":167,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ee92f6652b0350db9eb8ca7b84817a7d772b1c6c","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"早排HKU唔俾學生會播「地厚天高」，就係唔想大家得悉一啲歷史，一啲事。<br />\n<br />\n冇人會諗到當年嘅魚蛋社會大部分人都屌，去到2019勇武抗爭咁多人支持。<br />\n<br />\n我明白比起好多義士有人行得唔夠快唔夠前，但都希望繼續更多香港人覺醒，所有嘅義人平安。<br />\n<br />\n<em> 梁頌恆：「呢代人就似係鋪緊一條路，你當係條路從中環過海去尖沙咀。但每個人嘅力量都有限，只能夠搬到一兩嚿石頭只能夠鋪幾格，而且條路係單程路，鋪完你就要跳落海。但係後人可以沿著條路行落去，而且會越離越近終點。」</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJ2By5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJ2By5o.jpg&h=796ff8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y8z2-6uuaPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy8z2-6uuaPA&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e1681ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y8z2-6uuaPA</a>"},{"pid":"7c6c37f7d1422795777402ee533a0c513d04c312","tid":2398912,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a3e6d1ec62d252fb58f18eeaec8306fd1beaac","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"五年前，旺角魚蛋革命<br />\n三年前，陳同佳與潘曉穎赴臺旅遊"},{"pid":"06f9cf830ea3db02121b9914e167b5df0d9ec9ec","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6c37f7d1422795777402ee533a0c513d04c312","tid":2398912,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6600d7d83cc9c09cb0878253fb0bded1ca06a00c","tid":2398912,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fce43e2fd8f3f5d6c3196a38a8a77a502823d5ae","tid":2398912,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb85b6489fe141c3f40abd744cb021e4a06bc48b","tid":2398912,"uid":77717,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"莫嘉濤監禁4年3個月都係時候出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cab0c8a2fb18f0b291a5b9ad58ac2af532f658","tid":2398912,"uid":30476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"班仆街開實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fea78a89bc3c4a498bca33939f5a334d75681c","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"b8cab0c8a2fb18f0b291a5b9ad58ac2af532f658","tid":2398912,"uid":30476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"班仆街開實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.moonlol.com/wp-hong-kong-style/p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moonlol.com%2Fwp-hong-kong-style%2Fp3.jpg&h=b981038e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd8beccdc9e22567cab56d39937a5850d9d0e91b","tid":2398912,"uid":71657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"re