te><br />\n<br />\n每一個香港人都係要踩住前人嘅屍骨繼續行落去，過往香港人就係有太多道德潔癖，覺得踩住人哋屍體係唔光彩，係消費其他人，但要認清現實，只要想反抗，就要有不惜一切嘅意志，連道德枷鎖都擺脫唔到，又點樣同極權鬥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得香港人普遍對於踩住人地屍體上好心安理得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAuXiQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAuXiQO.jpg&h=d45c5720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adBZxaP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadBZxaP.png&h=4a526dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但絕對唔係一條越行越接近終點嘅<ins>單程路</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得，熱狗有時講得冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ea9e354534153eed746e4e576b1fa281e679d2","tid":2398912,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58d8b51c7555f9387eab223f7356f9e335fa58e","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66286f3001d157ccf02f4d50f5448a10de64031f","tid":2398912,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f5c5000e0f3634f942e31b7f45eed0f6a7aa28","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3657f5bd08bcc4a10d0b214005e98c7a820407","tid":2398912,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c88233c53837a5eb5af6daa2deafd3501a56e9","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb3657f5bd08bcc4a10d0b214005e98c7a820407","tid":2398912,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffff9de7dfecdb3cd05a2a213c60a010858f669","tid":2398912,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4558ee89e3850ba15eb2f23f5b6cc0b16acf1f","tid":2398912,"uid":78222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:08:04.000Z","msg":"練文嘅練文 武嘅練武 賺錢嘅賺錢<br />\n大家都等待一個時機 <br />\n我相信 總有日我地會再相遇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"直到煲底見"},{"pid":"2a41e51da151ad1107c7e1fe0bb9c782933686d8","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ffff9de7dfecdb3cd05a2a213c60a010858f669","tid":2398912,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4558ee89e3850ba15eb2f23f5b6cc0b16acf1f","tid":2398912,"uid":78222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:08:04.000Z","msg":"練文嘅練文 武嘅練武 賺錢嘅賺錢<br />\n大家都等待一個時機 <br />\n我相信 總有日我地會再相遇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"直到煲底見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"珍重"},{"pid":"5ce303316c77791e7642cc9eac631a3ce45ed91d","tid":2398912,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac25f73cc9637af50cdb749dec4bc30e936f3f4b","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"【香港命運分水嶺 &mdash; 2016魚蛋革命】<br />\n <br />\n五年前的2月8號，黑警大年初一晚上於旺角清剿小販，連市民大時大節吃魚蛋的權利也要剝奪。<br />\n <br />\n▍尤記得當晚看著新聞直播，目睹香港人反擊政權的怒火再燃，以及警察於鬧市開槍的狼狽舉動。<br />\n <br />\n奈何年初二早上醒來，個人在facebook上看到的卻是社會的兩極反應。<br />\n <br />\n因為不岔同儕對勇武手足的指責，對梁天琦等手足的責難，即使作為一個無名無姓的普通人，我在個人戶口寫下了支持本土派手足的看法，也掀起了和朋友的辯論。<br />\n <br />\n▍事實上，2016年2月8號是香港歷史其中一個分水嶺。<br />\n <br />\n那天，是繼2014年雨傘革命龍和道一役後，首次以各種進階手段，反擊對家無理打壓。<br />\n <br />\n那天之後，本土派出現史無前例的團結，出現#allin6 打出氣勢，全力支援梁天琦出戰新東補選。本土派繼而一鳴驚人。<br />\n <br />\n假如沒有那天，你不會看到《地厚天高》；魚革相關手足也不會身陷牢獄或流亡多年。<br />\n <br />\n最關鍵的是，沒有那天的話，天琦和over my dead body 對壘所引起的歷史漣漪很可能不會那麼廣，那麼深，那麼遠。2019年的香港革命也未必會出現。<br />\n <br />\n▍ 2016年的我們，遺憾地做不到「和勇合一」。2019年以至現在的我們，終於開始把「和勇合一」的精神刻進骨髓。<br />\n <br />\n縱使革命之事，不是一時三刻就能成功，但香港民族的進化，決無止境。念念不忘，必有回響。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n#Allin6<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112785760589838/posts/201974555004291/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112785760589838%2Fposts%2F201974555004291%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=38cb84fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112785760589838/posts/201974555004291/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"baf07fc51b9e2438ad42ea155ebfed9980f18716","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"【魚蛋革命五周年：本土抗爭的先驅者】 <br />\n <br />\n五年前的魚蛋革命，絕對是推動香港民主化的一場重要戰役。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，一眾抗爭者不惜犧牲個人前途，為香港拋頭顱，灑熱血，開啟了本土民主運動中不可或缺的抗爭面向。即使不是街頭鬥士，當晚全香港人也正在屏住呼吸，徹夜盯著螢幕上的直播。大家心裡也許是心痛，也許是錯愕，也許是憤怒，但無論如何，那時我們很清楚something is happening，香港從此變得不再一樣。 <br />\n<br />\n後雨傘時代，當時社會普遍瀰漫著一種抑鬱情緒。這種情緒，主要源於希望落空的強烈挫敗。就在這種氛圍之下，有班人身先士卒負起為大眾先行的責任，希望以行動衝破這種抑鬱情緒。魚蛋之後，香港突然出現一批政治犯。時至今日，有人已經刑滿出獄，有人仍然流亡海外，有人仍然承受牢獄之苦。<br />\n<br />\n記得有位魚蛋義士曾在獄中寄信出來，當中有一句特別深刻，意思大概是：儘管被人當鬼，心灰意冷，最後還是忍不住挺身而出，成為先驅。<br />\n<br />\n而先驅者很少自覺能以一己之力打敗老虎，而是一旦認定方向正確，就會覺得上山本身就是自己的任務，即使山中遇虎，也絕無遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n社會抑鬱催生先驅者，先驅者的任務就是找出脫離抑鬱的道路。路走對了，抑鬱者不再抑鬱，行動也影響深遠，任務超額完成。歷史亦都證明，他們是對的，只是先行一步。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，更多港人覺醒，但換來的是更高壓的白色恐怖時代。相比之下，後國安法時代的抑鬱情緒，比起後雨傘、後魚蛋看似更為嚴重。但不管如何，以行動衝擊社會抑鬱，從來都是我們的目標。念念不忘，必有迴響，成功之前，革命都不會有完結的一日。<br />\n<br />\n#魚蛋革命五周年<br />\n#念念不忘 #必有迴響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100206631386717/posts/459472205460156/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100206631386717%2Fposts%2F459472205460156%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=c3aa2e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100206631386717/posts/459472205460156/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3a6139230112e14e1e349dd1aa6e58f772717fb5","tid":2398912,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b57d320bafaac42540c5888b0d3427c5a61c34","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6139230112e14e1e349dd1aa6e58f772717fb5","tid":2398912,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b25f2dabe4e0e913c10ae6d5002f3e3b12bf6e","tid":2398912,"uid":54223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8cab0c8a2fb18f0b291a5b9ad58ac2af532f658","tid":2398912,"uid":30476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"班仆街開實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"開左先例現在已成常態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ea3467f4a94b5bbeca88f727081f1909664884","tid":2398912,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e308aa607032c6b152ab6074f8956e3423e4fe","tid":2398912,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"五年前<br />\n<br />\n大部分香港人<br />\n<br />\n冇揀 本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而系 民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnl-static.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/2016/02/lego2016feb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnl-static.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F2016%2F02%2Flego2016feb2.png&h=a8a7d251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">【2016-02-29 新東補選 全力支持6號梁天琦】黃毓民：民建聯贏關我叉事 9月本土派每區一席<br />\n2,490 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=x9I-9ZIZ6ek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx9I-9ZIZ6ek&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=86557c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=x9I-9ZIZ6ek</a>"},{"pid":"0e40b62fca62dc7fc0ea55b6e8a4c3a70eb38e0c","tid":2398912,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"黎明前嘅黑暗<br />\n係最撚黑暗"},{"pid":"1615c82419cc38454c442896fcfd66ab2e4401d1","tid":2398912,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac25f73cc9637af50cdb749dec4bc30e936f3f4b","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"【香港命運分水嶺 &mdash; 2016魚蛋革命】<br />\n <br />\n五年前的2月8號，黑警大年初一晚上於旺角清剿小販，連市民大時大節吃魚蛋的權利也要剝奪。<br />\n <br />\n▍尤記得當晚看著新聞直播