.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"嗰陣向天射，之後19年向人射<br />\n狗就進化咗，睇下你進步咗幾多？<br />\n如果未夠快就繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4ff6e2736674d08dea8e654dfc9e6570795618","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e308aa607032c6b152ab6074f8956e3423e4fe","tid":2398912,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"五年前<br />\n<br />\n大部分香港人<br />\n<br />\n冇揀 本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而系 民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnl-static.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/2016/02/lego2016feb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnl-static.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F2016%2F02%2Flego2016feb2.png&h=a8a7d251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">【2016-02-29 新東補選 全力支持6號梁天琦】黃毓民：民建聯贏關我叉事 9月本土派每區一席<br />\n2,490 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=x9I-9ZIZ6ek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx9I-9ZIZ6ek&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=86557c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=x9I-9ZIZ6ek</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實俾大家認清咗香港冇民主選舉，之後一步要點做先係關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ec97f53cbc44cc3b31e28bbbc6ec035fb5a7d5","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e40b62fca62dc7fc0ea55b6e8a4c3a70eb38e0c","tid":2398912,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"黎明前嘅黑暗<br />\n係最撚黑暗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"永遠記得天琦係台上面講呢一句"},{"pid":"632bb478c4ecc8c3e31e3dbdb6b8698eb37b4cf8","tid":2398912,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a80f42cc3f2eef82bef658822f7a86f817a1746b","tid":2398912,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"留家抗疫啦仲魚蛋"},{"pid":"98b339dec080c7682170156e309347931d6c9696","tid":2398912,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"魚革當年唔係香港<br />\n返到黎先知出大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caac5722d8984e36ffcc02a2d564ffca746c041e","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"632bb478c4ecc8c3e31e3dbdb6b8698eb37b4cf8","tid":2398912,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e02aa81dc8e16a7aa11da49251746665f9de04b","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a80f42cc3f2eef82bef658822f7a86f817a1746b","tid":2398912,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"留家抗疫啦仲魚蛋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"喺屋企食魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bed5fab72979a3fbb66cf7888f21d30205b633","tid":2398912,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b339dec080c7682170156e309347931d6c9696","tid":2398912,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"魚革當年唔係香港<br />\n返到黎先知出大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"嗰陣食完團年飯就上網見到旺角出椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4c4558ee89e3850ba15eb2f23f5b6cc0b16acf1f","tid":2398912,"uid":78222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:08:04.000Z","msg":"練文嘅練文 武嘅練武 賺錢嘅賺錢<br />\n大家都等待一個時機 <br />\n我相信 總有日我地會再相遇"}}